channel.title: Dellscape V2 Development Team (Reborn)
channel.description:
Ok, lately ive noticed people are saying that im a leecher that i suck at coding and such, ok well anyways im back into servers, now i will be only looking for testers and suggestioners, ill be making the client myself. And Please Read Everything Carefully And Keep This Thread Up, 5:11pm eastern time (start), 8:30pm (End Of Joining), And If You Are Accepted please pm me for more information.
[font=Verdana][i][b]Dellscape v2 Brought To You By The One And Only Dell[/b][/i][/font]
[size=6pt]Website Coming Soon, im waiting to recieve my bill for my domain. *Dellscape.com*[/size]
Dellscape Webclient: Coming Soon When i get my website.
Here Is The Client: Megaupload: There Both The Same. Coming Soon RapidShare: Coming Soon
Now We Have 6 Fully Working Worlds!
No Hamachi Required
Each World Will Hold Up To 150 people -Dellserver.no-ip.info- World 1 (coming soon) -Dellscape2.no-ip.info- World 2 (coming soon) -Dellscape3.no-ip.info- World 3 (coming soon) -Dellscape4.no-ip.info- World 4 (coming soon) -Dellscapestaff.no-ip.info- World 5 (Only For Staff, Mod, Admin, Chat Admin, Chat mods) -DellscapeMEM.no-ip.info - World 6 (Only If You Buy Membership)
Port:Default Port (Mems & Staff):Hidden
Status:Online Thanks To My Dedicated Server, You no longer have Lag, only at the max players of 132 is what i set it to.
-The Following Rules Apply To the Anti-Cheat In My Source-
Ingame Rules 1. No Cursing (Blocked Off, In AntiCheat) 2. No noclip (Blocked Off, In AntiCheat) 3.No setitem (Blocked Off, In AntiCheat) 4. No multiple log-ins (Blocked Off, In AntiCheat) 5. No stupid names like "~i kiil irl ~" (Blocked Off, in Anticheat)
Pking Rules ~ The Boundaries Are Only In The Wildy Itself ~ 1. No 0, 1, 2, 3 Item only pking (Blocked Off, In Anti-Cheat) 2.No Massing (Blocked, In Anti-Cheat) 3. No Double Teaming (Blocked, Admins And Mods Are Watching) 4. FarCasting Is Aloud, only because i fixed range 100% on my server. 5.No using ::bank during a battle!
Membership Rules (I Will explain more throughout later) ~ Same rules apply to what is in runescape ~ 1. Members Item Will say (Members only in f2p) 2. Members get items never seen before (Skill capes, Defenders, and secret areas)
Mod / Admin Rules ~ Mod Rules ~ 1.No kicking without my permission in-game. 2. No spawnings 3. No abusive powers.
Admin Rules 1.No kicking without My permession in-game.. 2.No banning without giving a request on this topic. Use The Following Format For Ban Request, everyone may use.
[code]I (INSERTNAME HERE) Is Requesting a ban request for (INSERTNAME HERE).[/code] Reason: Admin / Mod Shout Rules (I Will explain more throughout later) 1.No kicking without my permission.
Mini-game rules 1. Play Fair.
!Positions! You May Ask To Become A Mod Or Admin (Etc.) But You Must give a well written format.
Owner / Co-owner 1. Dell 2. Frell (Co-owner)
Staff: 1. ~ 2. ~ 3. ~ 4. ~
Adminship: 1. Weaving8 2. Kando2 3. ~ 4. ~ 5. ~
Modship: 1. ~ 2. ~ 3. ~ 4. ~ 5. ~
Adminship Shout: 1. ~ 2. ~ 3. ~ 4. ~ 5. ~
Modship Shout: 1. ~ 2. ~ 3. ~ 4. ~ 5. ~
I Will Soon Add Applications.
[size=24pt]Features[/size]
[size=16pt]Updates:[/size]
1. Lower Levels Dont Have To Right Click To Attack!
Dellscape v2 Features: Full Specials Full Fletching Full Wcing Full Runecrafting Full Crafting Full Fight Pits Full prayer With Head Icons Fully Working Range Fully Working Mage Fully Working Cannon used for pking! Full duel arena In Quest Tab There Is More Tele Areas And Your Pking Status.
~ Members Of Dellscape v2 ~ Once Ive Bought my Hoster to become public, you can purchase membership for my server for 1b on dellscape v2.
The Features you will recieve are amazing clients.. Skill capes Defenders Real story modes Full duel arenas And Many more, I Remain to keep these information hidden unless you buy membership.
~ Shout Information ~ Its Like ::yell, but there is admins and mods and stuff.. type ::shout (Words) then type ::Shoutbox to see what other people have typed Mods and admins can use ::shoutmute.
~ Money Methods ~ 1.Chop REg. trees for money, bronze axe spawns on floor east of training room. 2.Steal from tea stall. 3.Go to ardy and steal.
~ Runecrafting ~ This is the only way youll be able to make runes! type ::runecraft, enter the rift.. And start crafting airs, and work your way up.
~ Frog hunting ~ first type ::frog-hunt then type ::world and go hunt for the frog.
~ Fight pits ~ Tele to trollheim (Tzhaar) Then type ::beginpits and enter the pits, and kill the waves as the come.
~ Clans ~ Reserved ( Removed God clans) And adding better ones later.
~ Mehouse ~ Type ::mehouse Then type ::buildhouse and enjoy.
Here Are Some Commands ::Beginpits (Once your at fightpits) ::frog-hunt ::world ::waterbirth ::runecraft ::fishing ::food ::pvpon ::pvpoff ::mehouse ::buildhouse
~ More To Come ~
Pictures And Videos
Pictures (Coming Soon As Soon as I Get Alot Of People)
